{"id":302199,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-70余名上海维权人士就朱黎斌摔伤案到市政/","date":"2013-07-04T06:32:10Z","modified":"2013-07-04T06:32:10Z","title":"维权网 | 70余名上海维权人士就朱黎斌摔伤案到市政府信访（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span>，上海</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>余名民众在上海人民公园广场拉横幅声援朱黎斌：《上海民众呐喊：强烈要求政府承担责任和业务》、《为朱黎斌开通民政救助治伤费用》，大家到市政府信访办要求政府为其开通民政救助，朱黎斌在进京维权途中摔成重伤，政府有不可推卸的责任。且医疗费昂贵，其本人和家属靠吃低保生存，无力承担费用，政府必须承担责任和义务。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海维权人士朱黎斌带着上访材料于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>分</span><span>在上海虹桥火车站乘车欲去北京上访，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>米</span><span>高度摔倒，当场昏迷不醒。火车站警察把他送到长宁区中心医院抢救，医院虽然给予急救措施，但朱黎斌已全身粉碎性骨折，肋骨断裂插入肺部，由于没有钱，医院至今不给朱黎斌手术治疗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>时许，市政府信访办</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">115</span><span>接待室接待员接待了朱黎斌的声援者（详见照片《上海民众为朱黎斌呐喊：要求政府为朱黎斌开通民政救助治伤费用》），大家向市政府的接待员讲明来意：“朱黎斌因政府十多年不解决动拆迁问题而进京上访，途中摔下重伤病危。医生说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天之内必须要有钱动手术，否则有生命危险。今天已经第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天了。朱黎斌因家中极度困难无法承担医疗费，请求政府开通民政救济通道”。接待员推脱说转告到闸北区政府解决这个问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家立刻又赶到闸北区政府信访办，接待人员自称是信访办科长，姓张。大家跟他说了与跟市政府信访办接待时的相同诉求，张科长只是说向上级领导汇报，要大家给他时间，大家急切地表示，人命关天，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 10</span><span>天之内必须资金到位抢救病人，超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，后果不堪设想。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海维权者呼吁社会各界人士关注朱黎斌的生命健康权，关注访民群体的生存权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>朱黎斌妻子陆惠电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18017368638</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-mGApRcCGRdQ/UdT6rwE9kyI/AAAAAAAAkq8/BGa_2C-qfGY/s600/5.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-mGApRcCGRdQ/UdT6rwE9kyI/AAAAAAAAkq8/BGa_2C-qfGY/s320/5.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-sTsPlLxkx5w/UdT6tVDPa4I/AAAAAAAAkrE/jL54nWZWTQE/s600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%BA%E6%9C%B1%E9%BB%8E%E6%96%8C%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E5%91%90%E5%96%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%80%E9%80%9A%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E6%95%91%E5%8A%A9%E6%B2%BB%E4%BC%A4%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"190\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-sTsPlLxkx5w/UdT6tVDPa4I/AAAAAAAAkrE/jL54nWZWTQE/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%BA%E6%9C%B1%E9%BB%8E%E6%96%8C%E5%A3%B0%E6%8F%B4%E5%91%90%E5%96%8A%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%80%E9%80%9A%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E6%95%91%E5%8A%A9%E6%B2%BB%E4%BC%A4%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Jbrc-jlBPWY/UdT6vlNvebI/AAAAAAAAkrM/EVzndl9nz_s/s640/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BF%A1%E8%AE%BF%E5%8A%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%99%BB%E8%AE%B0%E8%A1%A8.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Jbrc-jlBPWY/UdT6vlNvebI/AAAAAAAAkrM/EVzndl9nz_s/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BF%A1%E8%AE%BF%E5%8A%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%99%BB%E8%AE%B0%E8%A1%A8.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-gQFcVHJfbRQ/UdT6ylAvd1I/AAAAAAAAkrc/I4qsjp6HGIk/s640/%E9%97%B8%E5%8C%97%E5%8C%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BF%A1%E8%AE%BF%E5%8A%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%99%BB%E8%AE%B0%E8%A1%A8.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogs